txt.en: Mablung wishes for you to travel to Haerondir and assist the Rangers there.
Anborn sees you approach and calls out to you
Anborn can be found at Haerondir in the Noman-lands.\n\nYou should talk to Anborn.
Travel to Haerondir in the Noman-lands, north of the Camp of the Host.

'[placeholder], Anborn and a handful of others have moved ahead to Haerondir, our fort in the Noman-lands. You can see it from here; it is the large ruin to the north. They will likely need any help you can spare preparing for the march into enemy territory.'
'Ah, [placeholder]! Good to see you. I take it Mablung sent you our way. We can surely use the assistance.'
